{"tid":1371790,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"如果新公司咁樣開價比你，你制唔制?","createTime":"2019-07-27T10:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T07:23:26.000Z","uid":57036,"like":2,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"314e5d2cc65d40bf7caa548cd260d075cdc9c3af","tid":1371790,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T10:10:25.000Z","msg":"當你而家每月搵緊$100<br />\n你叫20%，即係$120，新公司ok<br />\n但由於你舊公司係12個月糧+花紅<br />\n而新公司係13個月糧+花紅<br />\n所以佢開$110 (120 &times; 12 / 13)<br />\n即係頭11個月糧係打左折，最後一個月比番你<br />\n<br />\n你地制唔制?<br />\n制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2fd20d87f640751298e38c647ef3e7ebb92bbc","tid":1371790,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T10:33:19.000Z","msg":"唔好淨係比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講下點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a768aba6e275a1ad7c8404ce92eea4d6e116707","tid":1371790,"uid":152482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T10:36:42.000Z","msg":"你肯定你做到一年先走？<br />\n做唔到一年實收110<br />\n的確係高過舊公司，但你係咪趕住走，趕到唔可以等一個真120 offer先"},{"pid":"bbb2974d9dedbf8cd43529af561b4bcaf020fc93","tid":1371790,"uid":148224,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T10:37:29.000Z","msg":"花紅可以唔出"},{"pid":"c5e29e4baad996f2ea3f4ee4efcad3ba3bbf4cfa","tid":1371790,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a768aba6e275a1ad7c8404ce92eea4d6e116707","tid":1371790,"uid":152482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T10:36:42.000Z","msg":"你肯定你做到一年先走？<br />\n做唔到一年實收110<br />\n的確係高過舊公司，但你係咪趕住走，趕到唔可以等一個真120 offer先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":